data.description: Welcome Home! Amazing New Price for this beautiful move-in ready home in the highly sought out North Oxnard Seawind Neighborhood! This is the best value in the Seawind neighborhood! This charming 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home features dark laminate flooring throughout, newer kitchen appliances, dark kitchen cabinets that complement the granite countertops creating a contemporary aesthetic. With its 9-foot ceilings, this open floor plan feels very spacious and inviting and has lots of natural light throughout. The family room features an electric fireplace for cozy evenings.Enjoy the convenience of a separate laundry room, low maintenance patio, and direct access to two car garage. The extra long driveway is a popular feature of this plan creating more space for private parking in addition to garage and street parking. The manicured front lawn has eco-friendly turf that adds lots of curb appeal. Low HOA and NO Mello Roos! It is in close proximity to schools, community parks, restaurants, golf courses, Oxnard beaches & Marina, shopping centers, St. Johns Medical Regional Center and easy access to the 101 freeway. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity to make this your perfect home! Come tour it today!
